<div id="main_content">
	<h2>Football Game Day Update: South Florida</h2>
	
	<p class="article_info">
		
			By UCF Staff
		
		<span class="date">Sept. 3, 2008</span></p>
	
	
	
		<div class="article_img" style="width: 345px;">

			<img alt="Article Main Picture" src="../resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/1000/NE1543/en_US/bhcrop.jpg" height="226" width="345"  /> 
			
				<p class="photo_credit">Photo: Jacque Brund</p>
			
			<p>Fans are encouraged to arrive early for the Knights' 7 p.m. game Saturday against South Florida.</p>
			
				<p class="note"><a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=0024004102e146a9a011c28a8dadf0059ec">Full Photo</a></p>
			
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
		</div>
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
		
